Consider the following method signatures and corresponding descriptions. Assume that both methods appear in the same class.

Method Signature
Descriptionpublic int methodOne(int i, int j)Returns the value of  i + jpublic int methodTwo(int m, int n)Returns the value of  n - m

Consider the following code segment, which appears in the same class as  methodOne  and  methodTwo.
 int x = methodOne(4, 5) * methodTwo(1, 3);
System.out.println(x);
